  <content>The ##htmlcomment## macro is a bridge between Confluence and XWiki. It gives the possibility to add a comment in HTML code.

= Parameters =

|=Parameter|=Description|=Required|=Default
|**hidden**|Define if the comment should be rendered in the output HTML or not.|No|false

= Example Usage =

{{code}}
{{confluence_htmlcomment}}
it s a comment
{{/confluence_htmlcomment}}
{{/code}}

Result HTML:

{{code}}
&lt;!-- it s a comment --&gt;
{{/code}}</content>
